#Messenger
<a name="19035148"><br/></a>


In order have Oversec correctly process what's shown in in the Messenger app, you need to enable the option "Include not important views" in the "Lab" tab of the Messenger-specific settings in Oversec.

*Please do not attempt to use PGP Encryption with this app. PGP Encryá¹•ted messages are BIG and will need dozens of SMS to transfer.
Moreover, The Messenger app is known to crash occasionally when PGP encrypted messages with invisible encoding  are fed into its input field.* 

